title: Episode 364: Masturbation Theme Music (Feat. DaniLeigh)

description:
Singer/songwriter/choreographer, DaniLeigh joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her latest EP, "My Side." The ladies discuss topics such as: remaining friends with someone after you've had sex, why Dani hasn't been ready to begin dating again, their frequency of masturbating, and much more. Dani and the ladies even come together in prayer, seeking their perfect man. Enjoy!
